### ==========================================
### 栗藏 (LiCang) API 集成测试（完整场景）
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 插件运行
### 基础地址: http://localhost:8080 (网关)
### ==========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ==========================================
### 场景1: 注册 → 登录 → 获取用户信息
### ==========================================

### 1.1 注册新用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13900139000",
  "code": "123456",
  "password": "test123456"
}

### 1.2 登录获取 JWT Token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13900139000",
  "password": "test123456"
}

### 保存 token 供后续请求使用
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1.3 获取当前用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/user/info
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 场景2: 创建分类 → 用B站URL创建收藏
### ==========================================

### 2.1 创建默认分类
# @name createCategory
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "catName": "视频收藏",
  "sort": 1
}

### 保存分类ID
@categoryId = {{createCategory.response.body.data.id}}

### 2.2 用 B 站 URL 创建收藏（模拟解析后传入）
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "【教程】Spring Boot 3 入门到精通",
  "originUrl": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ABC123",
  "coverUrl": "https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/cover.jpg",
  "resourceType": 1,
  "platform": "bilibili",
  "content": "本视频教程详细介绍了 Spring Boot 3 的核心特性，包括自动配置、起步依赖、Actuator 监控等。适合 Java 开发者学习微服务开发。",
  "summary": "Spring Boot 3 入门教程，涵盖自动配置与微服务开发",
  "categoryId": {{categoryId}},
  "tagIds": []
}

### 保存收藏ID
@collectId = {{createCollect.response.body.data.id}}

### 2.3 创建第二个收藏（图文类型）
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "深入理解 JVM 内存模型",
  "originUrl": "https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/jvm-memory",
  "coverUrl": "",
  "resourceType": 2,
  "platform": "zhihu",
  "content": "JVM 内存模型是 Java 虚拟机的核心规范。本文详细介绍了堆、栈、方法区等运行时数据区域，以及垃圾回收机制的工作原理。",
  "summary": "JVM 内存模型详解",
  "categoryId": {{categoryId}},
  "tagIds": []
}

### ==========================================
### 场景3: 为收藏添加标签 → 搜索
### ==========================================

### 3.1 创建自定义标签
# @name createTag
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tagName": "Spring Boot",
  "color": "#1890FF"
}

### 保存标签ID
@tagId = {{createTag.response.body.data.id}}

### 3.2 获取所有标签列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.3 搜索收藏（关键词搜索，权重: title^3 > summary^2 > content）
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects/search?keyword=Spring&page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.4 搜索收藏（中文关键词）
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects/search?keyword=JVM&page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.5 获取收藏分页列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 场景4: 修改阅读状态 → 置顶 → 删除
### ==========================================

### 4.1 更新阅读状态为「在读」(1)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects/{{collectId}}/read?readStatus=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.2 切换置顶状态（置顶）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects/{{collectId}}/top
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.3 再次切换置顶状态（取消置顶）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects/{{collectId}}/top
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.4 获取收藏详情确认状态变更
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects/{{collectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.5 更新收藏内容
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects/{{collectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "【教程】Spring Boot 3 入门到精通（已更新）",
  "remark": "已看完第一章"
}

### 4.6 删除收藏（逻辑删除，ES 同步删除）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects/{{collectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.7 确认收藏已删除（应返回 404）
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/collects/{{collectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
